<br>
Ouch!! The above quote pulled down on my heart - dealt best with a wickedly loud scream...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>I couldn't think of words eloquent enough to describe my emotions but finally I wrote &quot;Spacecraft 107, alias Apollo 11, alias Columbia. The best ship to come down the line. God bless her.&quot; <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
